reeplugin.org" target="_blank">Free Plugin by SeoRoma</a></strong> - <em>Auto Tag Links</em>, <i>Changes</i> and<i> Plagiarims</i> plugins</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a href="http://www.whiletrue.it/cool-companies-using-wordpress-in-rome/">Cool companies using WordPress in Rome</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.whiletrue.it">WhileTrue</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://www.whiletrue.it/cool-companies-using-wordpress-in-rome/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"Winsxs folder: save space on windows server 2008 cleaning it";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:187:"http://www.whiletrue.it/winsxs-folder-save-space-on-windows-server-2008-cleaning-it/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=winsxs-folder-save-space-on-windows-server-2008-cleaning-it";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:93:"http://www.whiletrue.it/winsxs-folder-save-space-on-windows-server-2008-cleaning-it/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 08 Feb 2013 10:21:33 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s